message.body: Are you busy? Anna is breaking up with me and I don't want to be alone
Hey sorry. It'll be like 5 minutes. But if you can't or dont want to come over or need to eat dinner I can Skype with people
no, i didn't really have anything planned except tv, i'll be there in ~5 or 10
i'm home, no one murdered me. good night! it'll get better.
Yes! I'll probably be here for 30 more minutes
Sorry I just saw this! Lizzy just got here so I am hanging out with her while she unpacks some stuff. You're welcome to stop by if you want, and if not I'm sure ill see you soon (communal dinner?)
no problem. i think i need to get home, but communal dinner sounds good. I'm around, we'll find some time :)
